{"pageProps":{"slug":"/projects/timbre.soundfont.js","filename":"_pages/projects/timbre.soundfont.js/index.md","html":"<h1 id=\"timbresoundfontjs\">timbre.soundfont.js</h1>\n<p>A library that lets you play soundfont urls via timbre.js.</p>\n<p>Currently it uses the <a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/free-midi/\">free-midi</a>\nrepo to get it's sounds via jsonp.</p>\n<p>You can play all the instruments in the\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/General_MIDI#Program_change_events\">general midi standard</a> by\ndefault, or you can set a different url template, and pull sounds from your own site.</p>\n<h2 id=\"demo\">Demo</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://projects.skratchdot.com/timbre.soundfont.js/\">Timbre.js Soundfont Demo</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"dependencies\">Dependencies</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/mohayonao/timbre.js/\">timbre.js</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/audiocogs/jsmad/\">jsmad</a> - (If your soundfonts are in mp3 format)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/skratchdot/timbre.mp3_decode.js/\">timbre.mp3_decode.js</a> - (If your soundfonts are in mp3 format)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://mohayonao.github.io/timbre.js/src/extras/audio-jsonp.js\">audio-jsonp.js</a> - (If your soundfonts are on a different domain)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"jsmad.js\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"timbre.js\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"timbre.mp3_decode.js\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"timbre.soundfont.js\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"language-javascript\">\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// play note 64</span>\n  timbre.<span class=\"hljs-property\">soundfont</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">play</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">64</span>);\n\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// set instrument and play again</span>\n  timbre.<span class=\"hljs-property\">soundfont</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">setInstrument</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>);\n  timbre.<span class=\"hljs-property\">soundfont</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">play</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">64</span>);\n\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// only play if this note has already been cached</span>\n  timbre.<span class=\"hljs-property\">soundfont</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">play</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">70</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>);\n</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n","frontmatter":{"layout":"page","title":"timbre.soundfont.js"}},"__N_SSG":true}